OL,6,F"The first thing you notice is the
OL,7,Fsmell."
OL,9,FFormer steelworker and poet, Alan
OL,10,FDavies, melancholically remembers the
OL,11,FPort Talbot works in 1993 for the 'Way
OL,12,Fof Life - Steelman' programme on HTV.
OL,14,FHe had worked in the Port Talbot
OL,15,Fsteelworks for 14 years and throughout
OL,16,Fhis time there wrote poems about the
OL,17,Ftown.
OL,19,FOn Friday 19 January, at the site -
OL,20,Fits biggest UK plant.
